{"type": "article", "id": 29231, "title": "随身皮革口袋", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-06T22:51:55Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607062302572qKCV1Wb09ogf8DB.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>无论是结账时翻找钱包还是在需要其他随身小物时苦寻不见，都是让人觉得手忙脚乱而且尴尬的时刻，美国品牌 <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/HitchandTimber\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hitch and Timber</a> 推出了一款专门为日常小物而设计的小口袋 EDC Card Caddy，其中 EDC 正是 Everyday Carry 的缩写。它由巴尔的摩当地的工匠采用高级植鞣皮革手工制作而成，虽然外形有些粗旷但缝合处又不失细致。小巧的造型可以刚好放进衣物口袋，能够容纳最多五张卡片、小刀以及钢笔等小物。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/398923419/brown-edc-card-caddy-leather-card-wallet\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 46 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070623031147X8l3dZQjoKmBRz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706230311AXgsvjeiltDxBPEp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706230311BL6jrXnINq8POi9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706230313KJ4IHCUbTrPpN3RE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}